PHEZU kokuba uMasipala weTheku uthembise ukuthi izinhlelo zokuqoqa udoti zizoqala eMlaza kodwa izolo udoti ubusanqwabelene emigwaqweni yaleli lokishi. UNdunankulu waKwaZulu-Natal uMnuz Sihle Zikalala umemezele emhlanganweni obungoMgqibelo ukuthi bazoboshwa abazophazamisa izinhlelo zokuqoqa udoti. Bekulindeleke ukuthi amaloli akwaDurban Solid Waste (DSW) aqoqe udoti eMlaza ephelezelwa yizimoto zamaphoyisa kamasipala kodwa Isolezwe lihambele izigceme eziningi langawabona amaloli aqoqa udoti. Isolezwe lifike udoti usagcwele emgwaqweni kwaD, A,B, C, W, E,F, G nakwezinye izigceme. Ubungaqoqiwe ngisho ekuqaleni kwelokishi kwaV. UMnuz Jabulani Gwala, oyisakhamuzi saseMlaza kwaD, uthe kubaphoxile ukuthi umasipala ubathembise ukuthi udoti uzoqala ukuqoqwa izolo kodwa kuze kwashaya * -5 ntambama bengawaboni amaloli awuqoqayo. “Sijabulile uma umasipala ethi usezoziqoqela yena udoti kodwa asazi-ke noma ubedlala ngathi yini kwazise namanje udoti awuqoqiwe. Asiyithandi le mpilo esiphiliswa yona ngoba kuzoqubuka nezifo njengoba udoti uusunezimpethu. Size siwushise ngoba side lesi sikhathi ungaqoqwa,” kusho uGwala. UMnuz Dadashe Sosibo uthe umasipala kufanele uwuqoqe udoti ngoba bakhathele wukuphila nawo. Izolo kuye kwaba nombhikisho wabantu abebeqoqa udoti beqhubeka nokuwuchitha emigwaqweni yaseMlaza. UMnuz Msawakhe Mayisela, okhulumela uMasipala weTheku, uthe baluqalile uhlelo lokuqoqa udoti eMlaza kodwa kuye kwaba nokusatshiswa kwabasebenzi babo ezigcemeni zakwa-D, C nakwa-E. “Udoti uyaqoqwa eMlaza kodwa sibe nezingqinamba kwezinye izigceme njengoba kusatshiswe abasebenzi bethu. Sizosebenzisana namaphoyisa ukuze kuboshwe abaphazamisa ukuqoqwa kukadoti. Abantu baseMlaza bafanelwe wokungcono,” kusho uMayisela.